orm:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground\">Web platforms</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/68\">Marketing sites and application shells aligned with product goals.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 pt-0 sm:px-8 sm:pb-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-border/55 bg-background/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-foreground/60\">Design-aware implementation</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-border/55 bg-background/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-foreground/60\">Performance budgets</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-border/55 bg-background/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-foreground/60\">Accessibility by default</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground\">Design systems</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/68\">Reusable UI systems with careful tokens and operational clarity.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 pt-0 sm:px-8 sm:pb-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-border/55 bg-background/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-foreground/60\">Token strategy</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-border/55 bg-background/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-foreground/60\">Composable primitives</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-border/55 bg-background/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-foreground/60\">Visual consistency</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground\">Technical architecture</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/68\">Rendering, runtime, and delivery decisions that keep systems coherent.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 pt-0 sm:px-8 sm:pb-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-border/55 bg-background/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-foreground/60\">Cloudflare-ready deployments</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-border/55 bg-background/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-foreground/60\">Boundary setting</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-border/55 bg-background/40 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-foreground/60\">Runtime pragmatism</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><a class=\"inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-200 outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/40 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 border-border/80 bg-background/52 text-foreground/84 backdrop-blur-md backdrop-saturate-[1.4] hover:border-primary/30 hover:bg-primary/8 hover:text-foreground h-12 px-6 text-[0.95rem]\" href=\"/services\">See all services</a></div></div></section><section class=\"section-space\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"section-frame space-y-10 px-6 py-10 sm:px-10 sm:py-12\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-5\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-[0.72rem] font-medium tracking-[0.13em] uppercase transition-colors border-border/70 bg-background/52 text-foreground/62 backdrop-blur-sm backdrop-saturate-[1.3]\">Open source</div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">Open source is part of the operating model.</h2><p class=\"section-copy\">Public building blocks, clear contribution paths, and systems that stay legible outside the core team.</p></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground text-xl\">Public decisions instead of hidden tribal knowledge</h3></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground text-xl\">Issues and contribution paths that are approachable</h3></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground text-xl\">Tooling that works for maintainers as well as adopters</h3></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section-space\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-10\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-5\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-[0.72rem] font-medium tracking-[0.13em] uppercase transition-colors border-border/70 bg-background/52 text-foreground/62 backdrop-blur-sm backdrop-saturate-[1.3]\">Projects</div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">Capability shown through believable archetypes.</h2><p class=\"section-copy\">Public-facing sites, developer products, operational tools, and shared internal systems.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground\">Operational platforms</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/68\">Internal systems, dashboards, and shared platforms that support ongoing product or business operations.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground\">Developer-facing products</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/68\">APIs, tooling surfaces, documentation systems, and product experiences built for technical audiences.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground\">Open-source ecosystems</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/68\">Public packages, templates, starter kits, and integration layers designed to invite contribution.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground\">High-trust web experiences</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/68\">Marketing and product surfaces where clarity, credibility, and technical taste matter as much as polish.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-18 sm:py-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"section-frame relative overflow-hidden px-6 py-10 sm:px-10 sm:py-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden rounded-[inherit]\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-[-35%] h-px w-1/2 bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(67,45,215,0.95),transparent)]\"></div></div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 h-full w-full fill-current stroke-current hero-grid-mask text-foreground/12\"><defs><pattern id=\"_R_aglulb_\" width=\"44\" height=\"44\" pat